subversive and pretty arrogant

00:46:28.550 --> 00:46:31.870
about what Maimonides
thought he was doing.

00:46:31.870 --> 00:46:35.410
But, given his conception of
how information is organized,

00:46:35.410 --> 00:46:38.540
and the Talmud's conception of
how information is organized --

00:46:38.540 --> 00:46:43.030
the Talmud, information is chaotic.

00:46:43.030 --> 00:46:45.490
It -- it's created in conversation.

00:46:45.490 --> 00:46:50.190
It's like having an argument over
Thanksgiving dinner about politics.

00:46:50.190 --> 00:46:51.580
Beside that being a terrible idea

00:46:51.580 --> 00:46:53.630
and studying the Talmud
is a good idea.

00:46:53.630 --> 00:46:56.610
But -- but the -- the --
you start on one thing,

00:46:56.610 --> 00:46:58.490
and you think you're talking
about this that and the other.

00:46:58.490 --> 00:47:00.160
